http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10348/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10348/canvas/1/915d556a-f37f-484b-be48-03115f01e0a8","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:58:41.508Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds slowly walks up the stairs to challenge Alma. The stairway with its symbolic potential (rising and falling) is a central site of their relationship.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10348/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1410.2709288990836,315.58629587156,433.36439220183524,695.7067087155965"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10348/canvas/1/31e6d7e3-85ee-4990-a25e-b0c6596bac0f","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:59:04.573Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma’s dress, unlike <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW220238242 BCX0\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-04235.html\"><u>the one Reynolds designed for her</u></a>, does not have any white to represent the apron on her waitress uniform. Through her design, she is attempting to remove herself entirely from her previous subservient role. However, the shade of red is still the same—she is still tied to her past role, and he is still reminded of her “lesser” origins.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10348/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:360.03440366972575,85.71244266055076,260.4142775229359,688.2955848623855"}}}]}]}]}